# Local override PKGBUILD for xf86-video-intel on the "atom" (i686) arch.
#
# When config/packages/atom.toml marks a package source = "local", the builder uses
# THIS file instead of the upstream archlinux32 PKGBUILD, and an upstream sync will
# never overwrite it (see bin/lib/common.sh:pkgbuild_source_dir).
#
# Fork the stock PKGBUILD here, patch deps / bump pkgrel as needed, and the local
# copy wins. Placeholder for Increment 1 — real build logic lands in Increment 2.
